Throwback to a beautiful evening that marked the beginning of our journey with @auliglow — when #AuliSocials was born. Auli Socials wasn’t just an event; it was a space for honest conversations, skin stories, and soulful connections over good food and better intentions.
What followed was a journey full of learning, adventure and a bond we’ll always cherish.
Here’s to @auliglow — may you keep glowing like the brightest star.

#Throwback #AuliGlow #AuliSocials #MeaningfulConnections #GlowFromWithin

alT x B.C. SEN

What does financial independence feel like?
For her, it’s the pride of building something from scratch.
Owning a space that’s hers.
Paying her team. Paying herself.
Choosing jewellery not for occasions — but for milestones she created.

This Women’s Day, we celebrated women who invest in themselves — their power, their peace, their purpose.

#OwnYourStory #BCSenJewellers #alTxBCSen #WomensDayCampaign #FinancialIndepend #WomenWhoLead

alT x B.C.Sen

What does financial independence look like for the modern Indian woman?
It’s about choice, control, and the courage to build a life on your own terms.

This Women’s Day, we teamed up with B.C. SEN Jewellers to spotlight a single mother who invests in herself — so she can show her daughter what strength, self-worth and independence truly look like.

latestPosts.caption:
What an evening it was! What It Takes: Personal Journeys of Inspiration brought together stories that stirred the soul and laughter that lit up the room. From the heartfelt anecdotes shared by our incredible panelists - Aparna Sen, Rita Bhimani, Urmi Basu, Sharmila Bose and our very own Nandita Raja - to the spirited conversations with our guests, the evening was wonderfully woven together with wisdom, warmth and womanhood.

What made it even more special? Almost every woman present, came draped in her own beloved @kanishkas.kolkata saree - each weave a story, each thread a memory. Thank you to everyone who made this evening so unforgettable. Here’s to the journeys that shape us and the sarees that carry those stories forward.

Captured by @ayush_roy_art
